Night Shift:

Dirty Not Sorry Takeover

The Flamingo House – Sacramento, CA

July 10 | 9PM – Late | 21+





SACRAMENTO!!!!!

Dirty Not Sorry is taking over Night Shift at The Flamingo House with a stacked lineup from their collective.Dirty Not Sorry, one of the Bay Area’s most energetic crews, is heading to Midtown for the first time ever. That’s right — this is their official Sacramento debut, and they’re taking over Night Shift at The Flamingo House for a night packed with raw energy, heavy beats, and zero compromises.Known for throwing some of the most unforgettable parties in San Francisco, Dirty Not Sorry is bringing the full force of their sound to the capital city — and they’re not holding back.
